title: Sell
text: Select ac_mst_id, ac_name, ac_code from account_master

title: Purchase
text:
SELECT FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
       PARTY_NAME,
       Invoice_No,
       Invoice_Date,
       SUM(INVOICE_VALUE) INVOICE_VALUE,
       State_Code || '-' || State_Name State_Name,
       Reverse_Charge_Flag,
       'Regular' Invoice_type,
       DECODE(IGST_PER,
              NULL,
              (NVL(SGST_PER, 0) + NVL(CGST_PER, 0)),
              NVL(IGST_PER, 0)) Rate,
       SUM(Taxable_Value) Taxable_Value,
       SUM(IGST_Amount) Integrated_Tax,
       SUM(CGST_Amount) Central_Tax,
       SUM(SGST_Amount) State_UT_Tax,
       SUM(ADDL_TAX_AMT) Cess,
       DECODE(NVL(ITC_FLAG, 'Y'),
              'Y',
              DECODE(ITC_ELIGIBLE,
                     'IP',
                     'Inputs',
                     'CP',
                     'Capital Goods',
                     'NO',
                     'None',
                     null),
              NULL) ITC_ELIGIBLE,
       SUM(ITC_IGST_Amount) ITC_Integrated_Tax,
       SUM(ITC_CGST_Amount) ITC_Central_Tax,
       SUM(ITC_SGST_Amount) ITC_State_UT_Tax,
       SUM(ITC_ADDL_TAX_AMT) ITC_Cess,
       TRNO,
       GL_NAME
  FROM (SELECT F.FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
               F.FAAM_NAME PARTY_NAME,
               H.PARTY_BILL_NO Invoice_No,
               TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(H.PARTY_BILL_DATE), 'DD-Mon-RRRR') Invoice_Date,
               SUM(NVL(L.MATERIAL_AMT, 0) + NVL(L.IGST_AMT, 0) +
                   NVL(L.SGST_AMT, 0) + NVL(L.CGST_AMT, 0)/* +
                   NVL(L.ROUND_OFF, 0)*/) INVOICE_VALUE,
               DECODE(H.INVOICE_TYPE,
                      'RG',
                      'Regular',
                      'SEZ-WP',
                      'SEZ Supplies With Payment',
                      'SEZ-WOP',
                      'SEZ Supplies With Out Payment',
                      'DIM-EXPORT',
                      'Deemed Export') Invoice_Type,
               SUM(NVL(L.MATERIAL_AMT, 0)) Taxable_Value,
               L.SGST_PER SGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.SGST_AMT, 0)) SGST_Amount,
               L.CGST_PER CGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.CGST_AMT, 0)) CGST_Amount,
               L.IGST_PER IGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.IGST_AMT, 0)) IGST_Amount,
               L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER ADDL_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0)) ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               G.GMSM_CODE State_Code,
               G.GMSM_NAME State_Name,
               DECODE(F.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                      NULL,
                      'N',
                      F.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG) Reverse_Charge_Flag,
               
               NVL(L.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC, 'IP') ITC_ELIGIBLE,
               NVL(L.ITC_FLAG, 'Y') ITC_FLAG,
               SUM(NVL(L.IGST_AMT, 0)) ITC_IGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L.CGST_AMT, 0)) ITC_CGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L.SGST_AMT, 0)) ITC_SGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0)) ITC_ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               H.ACT_TRN_TRNO TRNO,
               L.ITEM,
               M.FAGM_NAME GL_NAME
          FROM IN_ITEM_HEAD    H,
               IN_ITEM_LINE    L,
               PP_PRODUCT_MAST P,
               GM_STATE_MST    G,
               FA_ACT_MST      F,
               FA_GL_MST       M
        
         WHERE H.TRNO = L.TRNO
           AND H.TCODE = L.TCODE
           AND P.PPPM_PROD_ID = L.ITEM
           AND H.ACC_TCODE IN ('PB')
           AND H.ACC_BILLNO IS NOT NULL
           AND L.ITEM_TYPE IN ('I')
           AND H.DELIVERD_PLACE = G.GMSM_ID
           AND F.FAAM_ID = H.ACC_ID
           AND L.POSTING_GL_ID = M.FAGM_ID
           AND H.COMPANY = 11
           AND INSTR(13, H.App_Branch) > 0
           AND TO_CHAR(H.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'MON') = 'APR'
           AND TO_CHAR(H.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'YYYY') = 2020
           AND H.PARTY_BILL_DATE BETWEEN '01/04/2020' AND '30/04/2020'
           AND F.FAAM_GSTIN_NO IS NOT NULL
         GROUP BY F.FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
                  H.PARTY_BILL_NO,
                  H.PARTY_BILL_DATE,
                  L.SGST_PER,
                  L.CGST_PER,
                  L.IGST_PER,
                  L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER,
                  G.GMSM_CODE,
                  G.GMSM_NAME,
                  F.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                  H.INVOICE_TYPE,
                  L.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC,
                  L.ITC_FLAG,
                  F.FAAM_NAME,
                  H.ACT_TRN_TRNO,
                  L.ITEM,
                  M.FAGM_NAME
        UNION
        SELECT F.FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
               F.FAAM_NAME PARTY_NAME,
               H.PARTY_BILL_NO Invoice_No,
               TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(H.PARTY_BILL_DATE), 'DD-Mon-RRRR') Invoice_Date,
               SUM(NVL(L.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT, 0) +
                   NVL(L.SGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0) + NVL(L.CGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0) +
                   NVL(L.IGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)/* + NVL(L.ROUND_OFF, 0)*/) INVOICE_VALUE,
               DECODE(H.INVOICE_TYPE,
                      'RG',
                      'Regular',
                      'SEZ-WP',
                      'SEZ Supplies With Payment',
                      'SEZ-WOP',
                      'SEZ Supplies With Out Payment',
                      'DIM-EXPORT',
                      'Deemed Export') Invoice_Type,
               SUM(NVL(L.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) Taxable_Value,
               L.SGST_PER SGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.SGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) SGST_Amount,
               L.CGST_PER CGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.CGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) CGST_Amount,
               L.IGST_PER IGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.IGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) IGST_Amount,
               L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER ADDL_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0)) ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               G.GMSM_CODE State_Code,
               G.GMSM_NAME State_Name,
               DECODE(F.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                      NULL,
                      'N',
                      F.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG) Reverse_Charge_Flag,
               
               NVL(L.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC, 'IP') ITC_ELIGIBLE,
               NVL(L.ITC_FLAG, 'Y') ITC_FLAG,
               SUM(NVL(L.IGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) ITC_IGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L.CGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) ITC_CGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L.SGST_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) ITC_SGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0)) ITC_ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               H.ACT_TRN_TRNO TRNO,
               L.ITEM,
               M.FAGM_NAME GL_NAME
          FROM IN_ITEM_HEAD    H,
               IN_ITEM_LINE    L,
               PP_PRODUCT_MAST P,
               GM_STATE_MST    G,
               FA_ACT_MST      F,
               FA_GL_MST       M
        
         WHERE H.TRNO = L.TRNO
           AND H.TCODE = L.TCODE
           AND P.PPPM_PROD_ID = L.ITEM
           AND H.ACC_TCODE IN ('PB')
           AND H.ACC_BILLNO IS NOT NULL
           AND L.ITEM_TYPE IN ('I')
           AND H.DELIVERD_PLACE = G.GMSM_ID
           AND F.FAAM_ID = H.ACC_ID
           AND L.POSTING_GL_ID = M.FAGM_ID
           AND H.COMPANY = 11
           AND INSTR(13, H.App_Branch) > 0
           AND TO_CHAR(H.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'MON') = 'APR'
           AND TO_CHAR(H.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'YYYY') = 2020
           AND H.PARTY_BILL_DATE BETWEEN '01/04/2020' AND '30/04/2020'
           AND F.FAAM_GSTIN_NO IS NOT NULL
         GROUP BY F.FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
                  H.PARTY_BILL_NO,
                  H.PARTY_BILL_DATE,
                  L.SGST_PER,
                  L.CGST_PER,
                  L.IGST_PER,
                  L.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER,
                  G.GMSM_CODE,
                  G.GMSM_NAME,
                  F.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                  H.INVOICE_TYPE,
                  L.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC,
                  L.ITC_FLAG,
                  F.FAAM_NAME,
                  H.ACT_TRN_TRNO,
                  L.ITEM,
                  M.FAGM_NAME
        UNION
        SELECT F1.FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
               F1.FAAM_NAME PARTY_NAME,
               H1.PARTY_BILL_NO Invoice_No,
               TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(H1.PARTY_BILL_DATE), 'DD-Mon-RRRR') Invoice_Date,
               SUM(NVL(L1.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT, 0) + NVL(L1.IGST_AMT, 0) +
                   NVL(L1.SGST_AMT, 0) + NVL(L1.CGST_AMT, 0) +
                   NVL(L1.ROUND_OFF, 0)) INVOICE_VALUE,
               NULL Invoice_Type,
               SUM(NVL(L1.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT, 0)) Taxable_Value,
               L1.SGST_PER SGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L1.SGST_AMT, 0)) SGST_Amount,
               L1.CGST_PER CGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L1.CGST_AMT, 0)) CGST_Amount,
               L1.IGST_PER IGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L1.IGST_AMT, 0)) IGST_Amount,
               L1.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER ADDL_PER,
               SUM(NVL(L1.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0)) ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               G1.GMSM_CODE State_Code,
               G1.GMSM_NAME State_Name,
               DECODE(F1.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                      NULL,
                      'N',
                      F1.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG) Reverse_Charge_Flag,
               NVL(L1.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC, 'IP') ITC_ELIGIBLE,
               NVL(L1.ITC_FLAG, 'Y') ITC_FLAG,
               SUM(NVL(L1.IGST_AMT, 0)) ITC_IGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L1.CGST_AMT, 0)) ITC_CGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L1.SGST_AMT, 0)) ITC_SGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(L1.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0)) ITC_ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               H1.ACT_TRN_TRNO TRNO,
               L1.ITEM,
               M1.FAGM_NAME GL_NAME
        
          FROM IN_SERVICE_HEAD H1,
               IN_SERVICE_LINE L1,
               PP_PRODUCT_MAST P1,
               GM_STATE_MST    G1,
               FA_ACT_MST      F1,
               FA_GL_MST       M1
        
         WHERE H1.TRNO = L1.TRNO
           AND P1.PPPM_PROD_ID = L1.ITEM
           AND H1.ACC_BILLNO IS NOT NULL
           AND H1.ACC_TCODE = 'SV'
           AND L1.ITEM_TYPE IN ('S', 'C')
           AND H1.INOUT_SERVICE <> 'O'
           AND H1.DELIVERD_PLACE = G1.GMSM_ID
           AND F1.FAAM_ID = H1.ACC_ID
           AND L1.CHARGE_POSTING_GL_ID = M1.FAGM_ID
           AND H1.COMPANY = 11
           AND INSTR(13, H1.App_Branch) > 0
           AND TO_CHAR(H1.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'MON') = 'APR'
           AND TO_CHAR(H1.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'YYYY') = 2020
           AND H1.PARTY_BILL_DATE BETWEEN '01/04/2020' AND '30/04/2020'
           AND F1.FAAM_GSTIN_NO IS NOT NULL
         GROUP BY F1.FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
                  H1.PARTY_BILL_NO,
                  H1.ACC_TCODE,
                  H1.PARTY_BILL_DATE,
                  L1.SGST_PER,
                  L1.CGST_PER,
                  L1.IGST_PER,
                  L1.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER,
                  G1.GMSM_CODE,
                  G1.GMSM_NAME,
                  F1.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                  L1.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC,
                  L1.ITC_FLAG,
                  h1.tcode,
                  L1.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT,
                  L1.SGST_AMT,
                  L1.CGST_AMT,
                  L1.IGST_AMT,
                  L1.IGST_CHARGES_AMT,
                  L1.SGST_CHARGES_AMT,
                  L1.CGST_CHARGES_AMT,
                  L1.ROUND_OFF,
                  L1.MATERIAL_AMT,
                  L1.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT,
                  F1.FAAM_NAME,
                  H1.ACT_TRN_TRNO,
                  L1.ITEM,
                  M1.FAGM_NAME
        UNION
        SELECT B2.FABM_GSTIN_NO,
               B2.FABM_NAME PARTY_NAME,
               H2.PARTY_BILL_NO Invoice_No,
               TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(H2.PARTY_BILL_DATE), 'DD-Mon-RRRR') Invoice_Date,
               NVL(L2.MATERIAL_AMT, 0) + NVL(L2.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT, 0) +
               NVL(L2.IGST_AMT, 0) + NVL(L2.SGST_AMT, 0) +
               NVL(L2.CGST_AMT, 0) + NVL(L2.ROUND_OFF, 0) INVOICE_VALUE,
               NULL Invoice_Type,
               NVL(L2.MATERIAL_AMT, 0) + NVL(L2.MATERIAL_CHARGES_AMT, 0) Taxable_Value,
               L2.SGST_PER SGST_PER,
               NVL(L2.SGST_AMT, 0) SGST_Amount,
               L2.CGST_PER CGST_PER,
               NVL(L2.CGST_AMT, 0) CGST_Amount,
               L2.IGST_PER IGST_PER,
               NVL(L2.IGST_AMT, 0) IGST_Amount,
               L2.ADDITIONAL_TAX_PER ADDL_PER,
               NVL(L2.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0) ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               G2.GMSM_CODE State_Code,
               G2.GMSM_NAME State_Name,
               DECODE(F2.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG,
                      NULL,
                      'N',
                      F2.FAAM_REV_CHARGE_FLAG) Reverse_Charge_Flag,
               NVL(L2.ELIGIBILITY_FOR_ITC, 'IP') ITC_ELIGIBLE,
               NVL(L2.ITC_FLAG, 'Y') ITC_FLAG,
               NVL(L2.IGST_AMT, 0) ITC_IGST_Amount,
               NVL(L2.CGST_AMT, 0) ITC_CGST_Amount,
               NVL(L2.SGST_AMT, 0) ITC_SGST_Amount,
               NVL(L2.ADDITIONAL_TAX_AMT, 0) ITC_ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               H2.ACT_TRN_TRNO TRNO,
               L2.ITEM,
               M2.FAGM_NAME GL_NAME
          FROM IN_SERVICE_HEAD H2,
               IN_SERVICE_LINE L2,
               PP_PRODUCT_MAST P2,
               GM_STATE_MST    G2,
               FA_ACT_MST      F2,
               --  FA_ACT_TRN      T2,
               FA_GL_MST   M2,
               FA_BANK_MST B2
         WHERE H2.TRNO = L2.TRNO
           AND H2.ACC_ID = F2.FAAM_ID(+)
           AND L2.ITEM = P2.PPPM_PROD_ID
           AND L2.CHARGE_POSTING_GL_ID = M2.FAGM_ID
           AND H2.DELIVERD_PLACE = G2.GMSM_ID
           AND H2.GL_ID = B2.GL_ID
           AND H2.ACC_TCODE = 'SV'
           AND H2.TCODE = 'SV'
           AND H2.ACC_ID IS NULL
           AND H2.ACC_BILLNO IS NOT NULL
           AND B2.FABM_GSTIN_NO IS NOT NULL
           AND L2.ITEM_TYPE IN ('C', 'S')
           AND H2.INOUT_SERVICE <> 'O'
           AND H2.COMPANY = 11
           AND INSTR(13, H2.App_Branch) > 0
           AND TO_CHAR(H2.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'MON') = 'APR'
           AND TO_CHAR(H2.PARTY_BILL_DATE, 'YYYY') = 2020
           AND H2.PARTY_BILL_DATE BETWEEN '01/04/2020' AND '30/04/2020'
        UNION
        SELECT B.FABM_GSTIN_NO FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
               B.FABM_NAME PARTY_NAME,
               V.FAAT_DOCNO INVOICE_NO,
               TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(V.FAAT_TRDT), 'DD-Mon-RRRR') INVOICE_DATE,
               SUM(NVL(T.FAAT_CRAMT, 0)) INVOICE_VALUE,
               'Regular' Invoice_Type,
               SUM(NVL(V.FAAT_AMOUNT, 0)) Taxable_Value,
               V.SGST_PER SGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(V.SGST_AMOUNT, 0)) SGST_AMOUNT,
               V.CGST_PER CGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(V.CGST_AMOUNT, 0)) CGST_AMOUNT,
               V.IGST_PER IGST_PER,
               SUM(NVL(V.IGST_AMOUNT, 0)) IGST_AMOUNT,
               0 ADDL_PER,
               0 ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               S.GMSM_CODE State_Code,
               S.GMSM_NAME State_Name,
               'N' Reverse_Charge_Flag,
               'INPUT' ITC_ELIGIBLE,
               'Y' ITC_FLAG,
               SUM(NVL(V.IGST_AMOUNT, 0)) ITC_IGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(V.CGST_AMOUNT, 0)) ITC_CGST_Amount,
               SUM(NVL(V.SGST_AMOUNT, 0)) ITC_SGST_Amount,
               0 ITC_ADDL_TAX_AMT,
               NULL TRNO,
               NULL ITEM,
               NULL GL_NAME
          FROM FA_ACCOUNT_VOUCHER V,
               FA_BANK_MST        B,
               GM_STATE_MST       S,
               FA_ACT_TRN         T
        
         WHERE V.FAAT_CGL = B.GL_ID
           AND V.DELIVERY_PLACE = S.GMSM_ID
           AND V.FAAT_TRNO = T.FAAT_TRNO
           AND V.FAAT_COMPANY = 11
           AND INSTR(13, V.FAAT_BRANCH) > 0
           AND V.FAAT_TCODE = 'BB'
           AND TO_CHAR(V.FAAT_TRDT, 'MON') = 'APR'
           AND TO_CHAR(V.FAAT_TRDT, 'YYYY') = 2020
           AND V.FAAT_TRDT BETWEEN '01/04/2020' AND '30/04/2020'
           AND B.FABM_GSTIN_NO IS NOT NULL
           AND (NVL(V.IGST_AMOUNT, 0) + NVL(V.SGST_AMOUNT, 0) +
               NVL(V.CGST_AMOUNT, 0)) > 0
         GROUP BY B.FABM_GSTIN_NO,
                  B.FABM_NAME,
                  V.FAAT_DOCNO,
                  V.FAAT_TRDT,
                  V.SGST_PER,
                  V.CGST_PER,
                  V.IGST_PER,
                  S.GMSM_CODE,
                  S.GMSM_NAME)
 GROUP BY FAAM_GSTIN_NO,
          PARTY_NAME,
          Invoice_No,
          Invoice_Date,
          State_Code,
          State_Name,
          Reverse_Charge_Flag,
          Invoice_type,
          IGST_PER,
          SGST_PER,
          CGST_PER,
          ITC_FLAG,
          ITC_ELIGIBLE,
          TRNO,
          GL_NAME
ORDER BY 4,3
